{"type":"message","id":"491fb242","parentId":"51a0bcd1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:00:02.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me summarize the findings for the user:\n\n1. **Gateway**: Running fine (pid 553990, state active, RPC probe ok)\n2. **Disk space**: 67G available (40% used) - no issues\n3. **Doctor warnings**:\n   - `plugins.entries.memory-core` disabled but has config (expected, since they've switched to OpenViking)\n   - Gateway service uses Node from version manager (`.n/bin`) which can break after upgrades\n   - Gateway service entrypoint mismatch - old path vs new path after upgrade\n   - Security: Gateway bound to LAN (0.0.0.0) - network accessible\n   - Session lock file exists (bea4541d...) - this might be the \"storage\" issue the user mentioned\n\nThe session lock could be relevant. Also the gateway service entrypoint mismatch suggests the upgrade didn't properly update the systemd service path. That could cause issues.\n\nThe memory-core being disabled and replaced by openviking seems intentional (per MEMORY.md they switched to OpenViking).\n\nI should report these findings to the user.","thinkingSignature":"f1531452ed76e69007ee31701f07c06ea46bb825a882e0e00c60021317602e3c"},{"type":"text","text":"检查结果如下：\n\n**✅ Gateway 运行状态：正常**\n- pid 553990，state active，RPC probe ok\n- 监听端口 18789\n\n**✅ 磁盘空间：充足**\n- 67G 可用（已用 40%）\n\n**⚠️ 升级后遗留问题（可能就是你说的存储问题）：**\n\n1. **Session lock 存在** — 发现一个锁文件，可能是之前进程异常退出留下的：\n   ```\n   ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/bea4541d-04c6-4924-b01b-68521919a3b8.js onl.lock\n   pid=554001 (alive)\n   ```\n   锁文件显示 pid=554001 是 alive 的，但这个进程和当前 gateway 不是同一个，可能有进程残留。\n\n2. **Service entrypoint 路径不匹配** — 升级后 systemd service 指向的还是旧路径：\n   - Service 指向：`.../dist/entry.js`\n   - 当前实际：`.../dist/index.js`\n   这会导致 gateway service 重启后加载的是旧版本代码。\n\n3. **memory-core 已禁用**（这应该是你切换到 OpenViking 后的预期状态，不是问题）\n\n**建议修复：** 运行 `openclaw doctor --repair` 可以自动修复 service entrypoint 问题。Session lock 的问题需要确认一下那个 pid=554001 的进程是否还活着。你要我帮你处理吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3324,"output":522,"cacheRead":12745,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16591,"cost":{"input":0.0009972,"output":0.0006263999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007646999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023882999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775631579289,"responseId":"06252fdb73a334d23fb702b96eff77e8"}}
