{"type":"message","id":"9a709d89","parentId":"d2f825a9","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:07:59.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me summarize the results.\n\n**After --repair:**\n- ✅ Service entrypoint fixed — now pointing to `dist/index.js` instead of old `dist/entry.js`\n- ✅ Gateway running with new pid (555433)\n- ✅ 0 plugin errors\n\n**Current data storage structure:**\n- Sessions: `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` — JSONL files, ~5.7MB total\n- Memory (LanceDB): `~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/` — ~76KB\n- Workspace: `~/.openclaw/workspace/` — ~1.2MB\n\n\n- Extensions: `~/.openclaw/extensions/` — ~142MB\n\nThe session lock appears to be legitimate — the lock file references pid 555433 which is the current active gateway process, so it's likely just a stale lock from before the upgrade that wasn't properly cleared.\n\nLooking at the session history, the lock file `bea4541d-04c6-4924-b01b-68521919a3b8.jsonl.lock` maps to `agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`, which is the current active session. The system is functioning normally despite this lock being present.","thinkingSignature":"39ce2d3320e0b89232b09c191c7958df9ce4da66778c928c06cc55daa273afd1"},{"type":"text","text":"**`--repair` 修复结果 + 当前存储结构：**\n\n---\n\n**✅ 修复确认：**\n- **Service entrypoint 已修复** — 现在指向正确的 `/home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js`（之前是旧的 `entry.js`）\n- **Gateway 已用新 pid (555433) 运行**，RPC probe ok，0 插件错误\n\n**⚠️ 遗留问题：**\n- Session lock 仍然存在（`bea4541d...lock`），但 doctor 显示 pid=555433 (alive) — 这个锁对应的是你当前的飞书会话（`agent:main:feishu:direct:...`），是正常的，不是异常\n\n---\n\n**📦 当前数据存储结构：**\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── agents/main/sessions/     ← Session 历史（JSONL），共 ~5.7MB\n│   ├── *.jsonl               ← 各会话的消息记录\n│   └── *.jsonl.lock         ← 当前活跃会话锁（正常）\n├── memory/lancedb-pro/       ← LanceDB 向量记忆库，~76KB\n│   └── memories.lance/\n│       ├── data/            ← Lance 数据文件\n│       ├── _indices/        ← 向量索引\n│       ├── _transactions/    ← 事务日志\n│       └── _versions/        ← 版本快照\n├── workspace/                ← 工作区文件，~1.2MB\n├── extensions/              ← 插件扩展，~142MB\n├── credentials/              ← 凭证存储\n├── openclaw.json             ← 主配置\n└── openviking.env            ← OpenViking 环境变量\n```\n\n**结论：** 升级后存储结构正常，memory-core 禁用符合预期（已切换到 OpenViking + LanceDB）。唯一需关注的是 session lock 如果后续持续出现\"stale=yes\"才需要手动清理。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10216,"output":668,"cacheRead":12745,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23629,"cost":{"input":0.0030648,"output":0.0008016,"cacheRead":0.0007646999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0046311}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775632055989,"responseId":"062531b84dd5ba2bc3c3af2ca283567d"}}
