{"type":"message","id":"1e3b90b4","parentId":"34c0d47f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:54:37.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying that LanceDB Pro was a community version they installed, not something that came with OpenClaw. They're just giving me context about the storage. Let me acknowledge this and see if they have any specific questions or changes they want to make.","thinkingSignature":"c60e054e0fe8185285d32a2c67c82908aed86a69156942faaa95289825a263bf"},{"type":"text","text":"了解。所以你是自建的 LanceDB，不是内置版本。\n\n那现在的存储栈是：\n\n```\nOpenViking (召回策略) + 自建 LanceDB Pro (向量存储)\n```\n\n这套搭配是合理的。如果有遇到什么具体问题（比如记忆召回不准、存储报错、或者性能问题），可以告诉我现象，我帮你排查。\n\n目前看 doctor 输出 LanceDB 正常注册了，如果没有报错就先跑着。如果后续有性能或召回问题，可能需要看一下 LanceDB 的索引配置和 OpenViking 的 recall threshold。\n\n有什么具体症状吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":25141,"totalTokens":25340,"cost":{"input":0.0000105,"output":0.00019679999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.009427875,"total":0.009635175000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775634867763,"responseId":"06253cb311f5e3e5f13011548dacd2c0"}}
