{"type":"message","id":"d60ab74d","parentId":"66f6ce6d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:21:37.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking two separate questions:\n\n1. Does the upgrade to 4.8 affect the GitHub backup strategy for the current storage architecture?\n2. How to solve the issue of me not responding to messages sometimes?\n\nLet me address both.\n\nFor question 1 - about GitHub backup:\nThe current storage includes:\n- `~/.openclaw/` - main config and data directory\n  - `agents/main/sessions/` - session JSONL files (~5.7MB)\n  - `memory/lancedb-pro/` - LanceDB vector memory (~76KB)\n  - `workspace/` - workspace files (~1.2MB)\n  - `extensions/` - plugins (~142MB)\n  - `credentials/` - credentials\n  - `openclaw.json` - config\n  - `openviking.env` - OpenViking config\n\nThe backup strategy should probably include:\n- `openclaw.json` - yes, config\n- `workspace/` - yes, important user data\n- `agents/main/sessions/` - maybe, session history\n- `memory/lancedb-pro/` - this is vector data, could be large, backup frequency should be considered\n\nThe LanceDB data in `memory/lancedb-pro/` is a SQLite-like or Lance format file. Backing it up is important but it might be large. The extensions folder is 142MB which is huge to back up - mostly plugin code that can be reinstalled.\n\nFor question 2 - sometimes not responding to messages:\nThis is about the Feishu bot not triggering replies. Possible causes:\n1. The gateway's RPC probe is ok but there might be an issue with message routing\n2. The heartbeat might be interfering with message processing\n3. There could be a subscription/notification issue in Feishu\n\nActually, thinking about it - when I didn't respond to messages earlier, it was because the system was delivering messages to me but I wasn't generating replies. \n\nThe core issue seems to be that when messages arrive, I'm not consistently generating responses. This could stem from the heartbeat check running at the same time as new messages, or there might be a race condition in how the gateway routes Feishu messages to my agent. The system instructions do warn against looping on subagents and sessions checks, so that could be creating a bottleneck where incoming messages get delayed or dropped.","thinkingSignature":"556ca1769f744a74acbd8e244d16cc867508479dea3d0181b2e4ee2bfb08470b"},{"type":"text","text":"两个问题分开回答：\n\n**1. GitHub 备份策略需要调整吗？**\n\n需要看一下当前备份了哪些目录。用排除法：\n\n| 目录 | 是否需要备份 | 原因 |\n|------|-------------|------|\n| `openclaw.json` | ✅ 是 | 配置，不能丢 |\n| `workspace/` | ✅ 是 | 用户数据和记忆 |\n| `agents/main/sessions/` | ⚠️ 可选 | JSONL 历史记录，较小时建议备份 |\n| `memory/lancedb-pro/` | ✅ 建议 | 向量记忆数据 |\n| `credentials/` | ✅ 是（加密） | 凭证，但需确认是否包含明文 key |\n| `extensions/` | ❌ 否 | 142MB 插件代码，可从 clawhub 重新安装 |\n| `lcm.db` | ✅ 建议 | SQLite 元数据 |\n| `openviking.env` | ✅ 是 | OpenViking 配置 |\n\n建议排除 `extensions/`，其余都可以纳入备份。LanceDB 数据增长后文件会变大，可以用 cron 定期备份而不是每次都同步。\n\n你现在备份用的是哪种方案？git push 到 GitHub 私有库？\n\n---\n\n**2. 消息有时候不回复的问题**\n\n这是 gateway 接收消息后没触发我的推理。可能原因：\n\n- **gateway 重启后 RPC 偶发抖动** — 刚才 `openclaw status` 有几次被 SIGKILL，可能是超时被 kill 了\n- **消息队列积压** — Feishu 消息进来后 gateway 处理延迟\n\n可以试一下：运行 `openclaw gateway restart`，让修复后的 entrypoint 重新加载，看消息接收是否恢复正常。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35,"output":816,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":25830,"totalTokens":26681,"cost":{"input":0.0000105,"output":0.0009792,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00968625,"total":0.01067595}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775636466699,"responseId":"062542f3b5f2fadadc3e0b4a9e3bb432"}}
