{"type":"message","id":"6ee3ceb0","parentId":"25356d0f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:14:27.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they have a coding plan (not the MiniMax Pro plan) and they're considering switching. They seem to be referring to their OpenViking/LanceDB setup and possibly the model they're using for embeddings.\n\nActually, looking more carefully - they said \"codingplan\" which might be referring to their MiniMax plan type. They might be on a \"coding\" or lower-tier plan that has insufficient balance for the embedding API calls needed by OpenViking.\n\nThey're considering changing something - possibly the plan, or possibly the embedding provider, or possibly removing OpenViking and going back to something simpler.\n\nLet me respond appropriately.","thinkingSignature":"657cfba306d234f79beb9bb48072ee75931c2bc8ed9f4f048901321e57ff958e"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，coding plan 的 embedding 调用额度有限，导致 OpenViking 的向量召回一直报错。\n\n如果你考虑更换/升级计划，有几个方向：\n\n1. **升级 MiniMax 计划** — 充值 embedding 额度，让 OpenViking 正常工作\n2. **切换 embedding provider** — OpenViking 支持其他 embedding 服务（比如 OpenAI、Jina 等），换一个有足够额度的\n3. **回退到轻量方案** — 暂时禁用 OpenViking，用内置的 memory-core（SQLite）先跑，等计划搞定再切回来\n\n如果只是想快速恢复回复，最快的方式是**临时禁用 OpenViking**，让 gateway 先正常流转消息。我可以帮你看一下当前 openclaw.json 里 OpenViking 的配置，帮你做调整。\n\n要我现在查看配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35,"output":293,"cacheRead":26646,"cacheWrite":9677,"totalTokens":36651,"cost":{"input":0.0000105,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.0015987599999999999,"cacheWrite":0.003628875,"total":0.005589735}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775643254989,"responseId":"06255d7785b2dd26fdd374b8c059591f"}}
