{"type":"message","id":"8b662ffd","parentId":"2bc76bde","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:41:22.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now the product-selector agent is configured to use Gemini 2.0 Flash. But I should note a few things:1. The `google-ai` API type might not be directly supported by OpenClaw's model configuration format. I need to verify if OpenClaw supports the `google-ai` API type natively.2. If the `google-ai` API type doesn't work, we might need to use OpenRouter which has Gemini models available.\n\nLet me inform the user of what I've done and the potential issue. OpenClaw's models.json might not natively support `google-ai` as an API type - it mainly supports `openai-completions` and `anthropic-messages`. \n\nLooking at the configuration, I specified `\"api\": \"google-ai\"` which may not be a valid type. The valid options are likely limited to `openai-completions` or `anthropic-messages`. If that's the case, we might need to route Gemini through OpenRouter instead, which has `google/gemini-2.0-flash` available.","thinkingSignature":"546b67b54455403496a4e42e6d54af2193f28856cc094964c54db72037539786"},{"type":"text","text":"已配置：\n- `models.json` 新增了 `google-ai` provider（Gemini 2.0 Flash + 1.5 Flash）\n- agent config 主模型切到 `google-ai/gemini-2.0-flash`\n\n**但有个问题需要你知道：** OpenClaw 的 models.json API 类型主要是 `openai-completions` 和 `anthropic-messages`，原生的 `google-ai` 类型可能不生效。\n\n如果 Gemini 跑不起来，备选方案是用 **OpenRouter** 接入 Gemini（OpenRouter 支持 `google/gemini-2.0-flash`），只需把 models.json 里的 api 改成 `openai-completions`，baseURL 保持 OpenRouter 的地址就行。\n\n你先试着调用一次选品 agent 看看能不能跑通，如果报 API 类型错误，告诉我，我马上切换到 OpenRouter 方案。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33282,"output":412,"cacheRead":12745,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46439,"cost":{"input":0.0099846,"output":0.0004944,"cacheRead":0.0007646999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0112437}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":177564487